        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">2</span><div><strong>If you smell gas, leave immediately</strong><p>Do not touch any switches. Open windows and doors. Call <a href="https://cadentgas.com/gas-escapes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;">Cadent Gas on 0800 111 999</a> first. Then call us on 0151 558 0334 once the property is made safe. Our first visit to make a gas escape safe is free.</p></div></div>
